{"id": "pos020", "name": "Audio_Xmas_688_12_24_1", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Bar_HeavenNote"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shop Owner"], "content": "Helena! Table 3! Stop spacing out!\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Ah...! Yes, sir! I'm sorry!\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shop Owner"], "content": "What's the matter with you? You don't seem very focused today. We have a lot of customers on Christmas Eve; get yourself together!\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Got it. Sorry...\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Apologies for the wait. Here is your order.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Customer A"], "content": "Thanks.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Staff A"], "content": "Your younger sister is staying at home by herself. You're concerned about her, aren't you?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "... I previously promised that I will spend today with her to celebrate Christmas.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Staff A"], "content": "You should talk to the shop owner. We can handle the rest.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "No... I can't do that. This is not an excuse. I will focus on the job!\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward »»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Staff B"], "content": "Little girl, you can't come in here.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">...... I, I'm looking for my sister...</font>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "......?\nAroma!? Why are you here!?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Because sister hasn't come back for a long time. I was worried...\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Sorry, sorry! I even promised that I would spend Christmas with you...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "You didn't even give me a phone call. I thought something bad happened. Thank goodness...\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "I am so sorry! However, as you can see, we have a lot of customers now. I really can't pull myself away from the line of duty. I don't even have time to make a phone call...\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "It's okay. I just want to know that sister is safe. There really are a lot of customers. It is Christmas after all.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Ah... You shouldn't come in here. Go home now. Sister will go back later.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shop Owner"], "content": "Ho? Isn't this Aroma? Haven't seen you in a long time~\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "G, good evening, sir~\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shop Owner"], "content": "Good evening. Did you grow taller again?\nHey, arrange a seat for her.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Owner? Is it really okay!?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shop Owner"], "content": "The routine checks are usually more loose on Christmas Eve. Should be fine.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "But...\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shop Owner"], "content": "It was me who asked you to work overtime and prevented you from going home to be with her. Let her stay here. You can be more at ease this way too, right?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Thank you so much!\nAroma, can you sit here and wait for me? My shift is ending very soon.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Understood. Sister, fight~\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shop Owner"], "content": "What do you want to drink? Uncle will treat you.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Then... o, orange juice...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Bar_HeavenNote"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "Helena！3番テーブル！\nボーっとしない！\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "あ……！はい！すみません！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "どうしたんだ？\n今日はずっと心ここにあらずじゃないか。\nクリスマスは客も多いんだ。しっかりしろ！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "はい、すみませんでした……\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "お待たせいたしました。お料理です。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["客 A"], "content": "ありがとう。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店員 A"], "content": "妹が家でひとりぼっちだから、心配なんでしょ？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……今日は、一緒にクリスマスを過ごそうって約束してたんです。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店員 A"], "content": "店長に言っておいでよ。\nあとは私たちだけでも大丈夫だからさ。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "いえ……それはダメです。\n言い訳しないで仕事に集中します！\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店員 B"], "content": "お嬢ちゃん、どうしたの？\n入って来ちゃダメだよ。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……お、お姉ちゃんに……</font>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……？\nAroma！？どうしてここに！\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "お姉ちゃんがずっと帰って来ないから、心配で……\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "ごめんね！ごめんね！\n帰って一緒にクリスマスしようって言ってたのに……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "電話もなかったから、何かあったのかと思って……\nでも、よかった……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "本当にごめんね！\nでもね、見て分かると思うけど、今日はお客さんがいっぱいで、どうしても抜けられなくて……\n電話する時間もなかったの……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "いいの。\nお姉ちゃんが無事ならそれで。\n本当にお客さんいっぱいだね。\nさすがクリスマス。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "あ……でもあなたはここには入って来ちゃダメなの。\n早く帰りなさい。\nお姉ちゃんも後で帰るから。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "お？Aromaちゃんじゃないか。\n久しぶりだな～\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "お、おじさん、こんばんは。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "こんばんは。\nまた背が伸びたんじゃないか？\nおい！この子に席を用意してやってくれ。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "店長？いいんですか！？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "クリスマスは取り締まりも緩くなるんだ。\nきっと大丈夫さ。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "でも……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "私が残業を頼んだから、帰ってあげられなかったんだろう？\nここにいさせてあげよう。\nその方が君だって安心だろうし。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "ありがとうございます！\nAroma、ここに座って待っててね？\nもう少しで仕事終わるから。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "うん、お姉ちゃん頑張ってね。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "何か飲むかい？\nおじさんがごちそうするよ。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "あ……じゃ、じゃあ、オレンジジュースを……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Bar_HeavenNote"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "Helena！三桌！別發呆了！\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "啊……！是！對不起！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "妳怎麼啦？今天心不在焉的？聖誕夜客人很多，精神點！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "好，對不起……\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "不好意思讓您久等了，您的餐點。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["客人 A"], "content": "謝謝。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店員 A"], "content": "妹妹一個人在家，在擔心吧？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……今天本來說好要陪她一起過聖誕節的。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店員 A"], "content": "跟店長說聲吧，剩下的我們來就可以了。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "不……那怎麼行。這不是藉口，我會專心工作的！\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店員 B"], "content": "小妹妹，你不能進來這裡喔。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……我、我找姊姊……</font>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……？\nAroma！？妳怎麼跑來！？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "因為姊姊一直沒有回來，我很擔心……\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "抱歉抱歉！說好要回去陪你的……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "連電話也沒打，我以為出了什麼事了，太好了……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "真的對不起！但妳也看到了，客人很多，我實在抽不開身，連打電話的時間都沒……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "沒關係，知道姊姊沒事就好。\n人真的好多喔，不愧是聖誕節。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "啊……妳不能進來這裡的，快點回家吧，姊姊晚點就回去。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "喔？這不是 Aroma 嗎？好久不見啊～\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "叔、叔叔晚安～\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "晚安啊，又長高啦？\n喂，安排個位子給她坐吧。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "店長？沒關係嗎！？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "聖誕夜臨檢比較鬆，應該沒事的。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "但是……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "是我讓妳加班才讓妳沒辦法回去陪她的，讓她待著吧，妳也比較放心吧？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "謝謝！\nAroma，在這裡坐著等我好嗎？我再一下下就可以下班了。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "好，姊姊加油～\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "要喝點什麼嗎？叔叔請妳。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "那……柳、柳橙汁……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Bar_HeavenNote"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["점장"], "content": "Helena! 3번 테이블! 멍하니 있지 말라고!\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "아... 네! 죄송합니다!\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["점장"], "content": "오늘 왜 이래? 정신을 어디다 두고 있는 거야? 크리스마스이브엔 평소보다 손님들이 엄청나게 몰려온다고! 정신 똑바로 차려!\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "네. 죄송합니다……\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "오래 기다리셨죠? 주문하신 거 나왔습니다.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["손님 A"], "content": "감사합니다.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["점원 A"], "content": "동생 혼자 집에 있는 게 걱정돼서 그래?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "…그래도 크리스마스니깐 오늘은 꼭 같이 보낼 생각이었는데...\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["점원 A"], "content": "점장한테 말이라도 해봐. 나머지는 우리가 알아서 할 게.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "아니야. 어떻게 그래... 그냥 핑계한 번 대본 거야! 자, 일하자!\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["점원 B"], "content": "꼬마야. 여기 함부로 들어오면 안 돼요~\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……저... 어, 언니를 찾으러 왔는데……</font>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……？\nAroma！？여긴 어떻게 온 거야！？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "언니가 자꾸 집에 안 오니깐... 걱정돼서....\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "정말 미안해! 크리스마스 같이 보내자고 먼저 말해놓고는....\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "전화도 연결이 안 되고... 무슨 일이 난 줄만 알아서... 다행이야....\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "진짜 미안해! 너도 봤겠지만 손님들이 너무 많아서... 따로 전화하거나 그럴 시간도 없었어...\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "언니가 무사하다는 거 알았으면 그걸로 괜찮아.\n사람 진짜 많다! 역시 크리스마스이긴 한가 보네.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "음……원래는 여기 들어오면 안 돼. 그러니깐 얼른 집에 가있어. 언니는 조금 늦게 집에 들어갈 것 같아.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["점장"], "content": "응? Aroma 아니니? 오랜만이로구나~\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "아, 안녕하세요 아저씨.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["점장"], "content": "그래~ 못 본 새 또 큰 것 같구나?\n저기, 이 아이 자리 좀 마련해줘\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "점장님? 그래도 괜찮은 건가요!?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["점장"], "content": "크리스마스이브 같은 날엔 오히려 단속이 덜 심할 때도 많거든. 괜찮을 거다.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "하지만……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["점장"], "content": "네가 저 애랑 같이 있어 주지 못한 것도 내가 너한테 잔업을 맡겨서 그런 거잖아. 그냥 옆에 앉혀 두는 게 너도 더 안심될 테지?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "감사합니다!\nAroma, 여기 잠깐만 앉아 있을래? 조금만 더 하면 퇴근이니깐 여기 앉아서 기다리고 있어.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "알았어! 언니 힘내~\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["점장"], "content": "뭐 마실 거라도 줄까? 아저씨가 서비스로 줄게!\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "그럼...오...오렌지 주스로...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Bar_HeavenNote"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "Helena！三桌！別發呆了！\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "啊……！是！對不起！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "妳怎麼啦？今天心不在焉的？聖誕夜客人很多，精神點！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "好，對不起……\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "不好意思讓您久等了，您的餐點。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["客人 A"], "content": "謝謝。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店員 A"], "content": "妹妹一個人在家，在擔心吧？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……今天本來說好要陪她一起過聖誕節的。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店員 A"], "content": "跟店長說聲吧，剩下的我們來就可以了。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "不……那怎麼行。這不是藉口，我會專心工作的！\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店員 B"], "content": "小妹妹，你不能進來這裡喔。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……我、我找姊姊……</font>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……？\nAroma！？妳怎麼跑來！？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "因為姊姊一直沒有回來，我很擔心……\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "抱歉抱歉！說好要回去陪你的……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "連電話也沒打，我以為出了什麼事了，太好了……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "真的對不起！但妳也看到了，客人很多，我實在抽不開身，連打電話的時間都沒……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "沒關係，知道姊姊沒事就好。\n人真的好多喔，不愧是聖誕節。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "啊……妳不能進來這裡的，快點回家吧，姊姊晚點就回去。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "喔？這不是 Aroma 嗎？好久不見啊～\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "叔、叔叔晚安～\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "晚安啊，又長高啦？\n喂，安排個位子給她坐吧。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "店長？沒關係嗎！？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "聖誕夜臨檢比較鬆，應該沒事的。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "但是……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "是我讓妳加班才讓妳沒辦法回去陪她的，讓她待著吧，妳也比較放心吧？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "謝謝！\nAroma，在這裡坐著等我好嗎？我再一下下就可以下班了。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "好，姊姊加油～\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "要喝點什麼嗎？叔叔請妳。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "那……柳、柳橙汁……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Bar_HeavenNote"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店长"], "content": "Helena！三桌！别发呆了！\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "啊……！是！对不起！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店长"], "content": "妳怎么啦？今天心不在焉的？圣诞夜客人很多，精神点！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "好，对不起……\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "不好意思让您久等了，您的餐点。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["客人 A"], "content": "谢谢。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店员 A"], "content": "妹妹一个人在家，在担心吧？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["H